txt.en: 'While a tent is not a house, there are still some things that can be done to add some comfort and turn it into a home. Beds, tables, camp-fires, and stools are among the things that we can add to help return a semblance of normalcy to people's lives.'
'Hytbold is one step closer to being rebuilt and restored.'
There is much work to do to rebuild the town of Hytbold.
